# ------------------------------- start web storage attack scenarios ------------------------------- # 
    # ------- manipulate storage values attack scenario:
        Could allows the attacker to hijacking session.

    # ------- XSS session values access attack scenario:
        web storage values accessiable by Javascript, which allows the attacker to access web storage containers with XSS.
